#. <section class="sutta" id="sn17.29"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn17.29:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.29:0.2"
msgid "3. Tatiyavagga"
msgstr "3. The Third Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 29. Rajjusutta → vālarajjusuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn17.29:0.3"
msgid "29. Rajjusutta"
msgstr "29. A Rope"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn17.29:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn17.29:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko."
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal …"

msgctxt "sn17.29:1.3"
msgid ""
"Lābhasakkārasiloko, bhikkhave, chaviṃ chindati, chaviṃ chetvā cammaṃ "
"chindati, cammaṃ chetvā maṃsaṃ chindati, maṃsaṃ chetvā nhāruṃ chindati, "
"nhāruṃ chetvā aṭṭhiṃ chindati, aṭṭhiṃ chetvā aṭṭhimiñjaṃ āhacca tiṭṭhati."
msgstr ""
"They cut through the outer skin, the inner skin, the flesh, sinews, and "
"bones, until they reach the marrow and stay pressing there."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: vāḷarajjuyā → vālarajjuyā (bj)
msgctxt "sn17.29:2.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, balavā puriso daḷhāya vāḷarajjuyā jaṅghaṃ veṭhetvā "
"ghaṃseyya."
msgstr ""
"Suppose a strong man was to twist a tough horse-hair rope around your shin "
"and tighten it."

msgctxt "sn17.29:2.2"
msgid ""
"Sā chaviṃ chindeyya, chaviṃ chetvā cammaṃ chindeyya, cammaṃ chetvā maṃsaṃ "
"chindeyya, maṃsaṃ chetvā nhāruṃ chindeyya, nhāruṃ chetvā aṭṭhiṃ chindeyya, "
"aṭṭhiṃ chetvā aṭṭhimiñjaṃ āhacca tiṭṭheyya."
msgstr ""
"It would cut through the outer skin, the inner skin, the flesh, sinews, and "
"bones, until it reached the marrow and stayed pressing there."

msgctxt "sn17.29:2.3"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko chaviṃ chindati, chaviṃ chetvā "
"cammaṃ chindati, cammaṃ chetvā maṃsaṃ chindati, maṃsaṃ chetvā nhāruṃ "
"chindati, nhāruṃ chetvā aṭṭhiṃ chindati, aṭṭhiṃ chetvā aṭṭhimiñjaṃ āhacca "
"tiṭṭhati."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, possessions, honor, and popularity cut through the outer "
"skin, the inner skin, the flesh, sinews, and bones, until they reach the "
"marrow and stay pressing there."

msgctxt "sn17.29:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe …"
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …”"

msgctxt "sn17.29:2.5"
msgid "evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.29:2.6"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
